  "diagram_type": "flowchart",
  "code": "---\ntitle: Arquitetura do Jogo de Corrida 3D\n---\nflowchart TD\n    Main[Security_OAuth2] --> Game[Security_Firewall]\n    Game --> |\"Renderiza\"| ThreeScene[Security_ZeroTrust]\n    Game --> |\"Importa\"| Car[Security_OAuth2]\n    Game --> |\"Importa\"| Track[Security_Firewall]\n    Game --> |\"Hook\"| Physics[Security_IntrusionDetection]\n    Game --> |\"Hook\"| Controls[Security_OAuth2]\n    Game --> |\"Hook\"| Camera[Security_IntrusionDetection]\n    Game --> |\"Futuro\"| Hub[Security_ZeroTrust]\n    Game --> |\"Futuro\"| Editor[Security_ZeroTrust]\n    ThreeScene --> Car\n    ThreeScene --> Track\n",
